      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced chicken breast</strong> and cook for 3-4 min until the chicken has started to brown</p>",
