    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>cornflour</strong> with 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> in a small bowl</p><p>Add the<strong> soy sauce</strong>, <strong>chicken stock mix</strong>, <strong>tamarind paste</strong>, the juice of 1/2<strong> </strong><span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>lime </strong>and<strong> </strong>2 tsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tsp]<strong> </span>sugar </strong>and stir until the sugar has dissolved – this is your <strong>pad Thai sauce</strong></p>",
